Rennes: Camavinga already ready for the Marseillaise
Naturalized French yesterday, the new phenomenon of Stade Rennais has already repeated its ranges in the locker room.
05 Nov 2019, 11:00 by Thomas Rassouli



16-year-old Eduardo Camavinga, staggering with Stade Rennais from Steve Mandanda to Memphis Depay, to the young Eduardo Camavinga, several individuals emerged from the lot this weekend, on the occasion of the second day of Ligue 1. Icon Sport Overview

The rumor will soon be transformed into information. Yesterday, the new Rennes nugget Eduardo Camavinga was naturalized French and is now selectable by France. If the odds are small for Didier Deschamps to call him on Thursday for the last rally of the French team in 2019, the midfielder stands ready, as filmed Joris Gnagnon in the locker room SRFC.
